            "id": 5943519,
            "title": "〈台股開盤〉台積電法說釋定心丸 早盤漲逾百點挑戰19500大關",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>台積電 17 日法說會展望亮眼，帶動台股今 (18) 日開高走高，開 19423.98 點，上漲 85.25 點，持續上漲漲逾 100 點，不過在關稅不確定性持續，一度賣壓湧現漲幅收斂，而在台積電、聯發科等權值股撐盤下，指數再度上攻，挑戰 19500 大關。早盤估量 2396 億元，較前一日量縮。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>電子權值股漲跌互現，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:TSM:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/TSM\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">TSM-US</a>) 漲 8 元，漲約 1%，來到 855 元；聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 漲 10 元，漲約 1%，來到 1350 元；鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 持平，廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 跌近 1%、日月光投控 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>)、聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>) 於平盤上方。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>航運類股成今日盤面亮點，中櫃 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2613:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2613\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2613-TW</a>) 亮紅燈，萬海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2615:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2615\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2615-TW</a>) 漲逾 5%，四維航 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5608:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5608\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5608-TW</a>) 漲約 3%，陽明 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2609:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2609\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2609-TW</a>) 漲約 2%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>記憶體產業因關稅，出現備貨熱潮，相關類股走強，南亞科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>) 漲約 3%，創見 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2451:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2451\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2451-TW</a>) 漲約 2%，華邦電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2344:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2344\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2344-TW</a>)、創意 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3443:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3443\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3443-TW</a>) 均漲逾 1%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>總統賴清德日前宣稱打造資安國家隊，帶動資服股走強，資通 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2471:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2471\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2471-TW</a>) 漲逾 8%，邁達特 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6112:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6112\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6112-TW</a>) 漲逾 2%，凌群 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2453:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2453\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2453-TW</a>) 漲逾 1%，零壹 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3029:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3029\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3029-TW</a>) 漲約 1%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
